Package it.polimi.ingsw

Class ClientCLIMain

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.ClientCLIMain
public class ClientCLIMain
extends java.lang.Object
Class used to initialize CLI Game. Main for players who want to play with CLI. It interacts with ConnectionMangerSocket to save starting parameters game and it is active until Game ends.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors 
    Constructor Description
    ClientCLIMain()
    ClientCLIMain constructor, it calls all methods to manages starting parameters choice: IP server, Player nickname, three or two players match, player color and cards choice.
